      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is a commercially validated FEA solver with documented QA processes, ISO 9001 certification, and release verification testing. FDA in-house code underwent independent verification. Required level 2 is met by demonstrated solver pedigree and documented test suite results."
