      "rationale": "Stiffness: 4.2% difference, E/uval = 0.81. Yield force: 6.7% difference, E/uval = 1.34. Force at 40 mm: 3.9% difference, E/uval = 0.74. All three QoIs satisfy acceptance bounds. Force-displacement curves show good morphological agreement throughout the loading range."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
