      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the standard ASTM F1717 metrics and are directly relevant to the clinical concern of implant mechanical integrity under physiological bending loads. The QoIs are unambiguously connected to the COU intended use."
