    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility evidence package for COU1 is judged sufficient to support the Accepted decision. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors achieved or exceeded their required levels. The overall pattern of evidence, including strong output comparison metrics (all QoIs within 10%, all E/uval below 1.96), independent laboratory replication, and documented mesh convergence, provides adequate confidence in the FEA predictions for the intended use. The credibility team concluded that the model is fit for purpose within the scope of COU1.",
